
<h1>We'd like to get to know you</h1>

<form id="update-form">

<div class="genderContainer">

    <p>What is your gender?</p>
    <input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="female" {{radioBtnHelper 'female' user.survey.gender}}>
    <label for="female">Female</label><br>
    <input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="male" {{radioBtnHelper 'male' user.survey.gender}}>
    <label for="male">Male</label><br>
    {{!-- <input type="radio" id="anyone" name="gender" value="prefer not to say" {{radioBtnHelper 'prefer not to say'
        user.survey.gender}}>
    <label for="anyone">Prefer not to say</label> --}}

</div>
    <br>
    <br>

    <p>Who would you like to see on this site?</p>
    <input type="radio" id="prefer_female" name="pref_gender" value="female" {{radioBtnHelper 'female'
        user.survey.pref_gender}}>
    <label for="prefer_female">Female</label><br>
    <input type="radio" id="prefer_male" name="pref_gender" value="male" {{radioBtnHelper 'male'
        user.survey.pref_gender}}>
    <label for="prefer_male">Male</label><br>
    <input type="radio" id="prefer_anyone" name="pref_gender" value="anyone" {{radioBtnHelper 'anyone'
        user.survey.pref_gender}}>
    <label for="prefer_anyone">Anyone</label>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>What is your birthdate?</p>
    <input type="date" id="birthdate" name="birthdate" value={{user.survey.birthdate}}>
    <label for="birthdate">Birthdate as MM/DD/YYYY</label><br>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>Why are you joining this dating site?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="goal" name="goal" >{{user.survey.goal}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>Relationship-wise, how do you see yourself in the future?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="relationship" name="relationship" >{{user.survey.relationship}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>What type of programmer are you?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="programmer_type" name="programmer_type" >{{user.survey.programmer_type}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>What is your favorite programming language?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="language" name="language" >{{user.survey.language}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>How would you describe your work ethic?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="worker" name="worker" >{{user.survey.worker}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <p>What is your ideal date night?</p>
    <textarea rows="4" cols="50" id="ideal_date" name="ideal_date" >{{user.survey.ideal_date}}</textarea>

    <p>A brief self-introduction</p>
    <textarea id="bio" name="bio" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="Talk a bit more about yourself" >{{user.survey.bio}}</textarea>

    <br>
    <br>

    <button>Update</button>
    <a href="/profile">Cancel</a>
</form>

<script src="/js/profile.js"></script>